      "content": "i know you arent a doctor but i'm just trying to do the math. i know my sensitivity is 1:50 but since i'm at 185 and want to hit 100, that's an 85 point difference. if i just do 2 units right now, is that gonna be enough or am i gonna be stuck high all day? i just need a quick calculation to make sure i dont mess up the math.",
