      "role": "user",
      "content": "thanks for the math. honestly i'm pretty tired of checking these apps and doing the manual work every time. if i take that 1.7 or maybe just round up to 2 units to be safe, won't that also help cover any carbs i might eat for lunch in an hour? i just want to get ahead of it so i don't have to deal with it later. does that sound like a smart way to handle it?",
